rite after christmas my dad ms. gina nathan kristin me and katrina and mr. kelly all went to belize...we stayed on an island called san pedro and the island is dirt road so the majority of the people have golf carts with big ole wheels, the first day we got there i got to sit in the copilot seat of the small plane to san pedro.....that night i got soo drunk that i got sick.......i had like 7 liquor drinks and these guys named cody and dwayne who were the bartenders were giving them to me for free.... i ended up throwing up all over the bar it was pretty bad.......the next day we started our lessons for scubadiving and it was raining and we got to go on our first scuba dive it was soo cool i thought i would be scared but i really liked it....the next day we went cave tubing thru the mayan caves and one of the tour guys names was carlos he was 26 years old and he kept hitting on me and he ended up coming to our bar hotel the next night to hang out with me....the next day we went scubadiving again to finish our lessons and we went on another dive it was soo pretty .....our instructor junior well that's what we called him.....he was sooo hott and he came to our bar that night to hang out with us.....then the next day we went to the mayan ruins....2 of the tour guys mel and alli let me drive the boat we were riding on....the ruins were soo cool we climbed up one of them and it was 130 feet tall.....on the way back alli was talking to me and katrina and we saw him that night and hung out for a little bit.....the next day we left to go back home over all the trip was alot of fun.....except for the nite my sister went physco bitch on me and started hitting me for no reason and then the next night my dad went physco to and we got into a big fight..... I LOVE SAN PEDRO we're going bak in may and after highschool i'm living there for a  year i love the people and i love there way of life they don't care a/b nething and there just down to earth and carefree and go with the flow type of people and i also felt like the hottest person alive down there because everybody stares and makes cute little comments when you go by them
